=== EARTH_SANCTUM ===
# id: 82
# title: The Earth Sanctum
# chinese_title: 大地圣所
# category: Shrine
# mode: dungeon

A chamber filled with actual soil — a rarity in space. Plants grow under artificial sunlight, their roots visible through transparent walls. The soil has been arranged in patterns resembling Chinese characters, tended by an automated gardening system still faithfully at work.

* [Plant a seed and make a wish]
  ~ gain_radical("土")
  "土" (tǔ) — earth, soil, ground
* [Harvest some of the ripe plants]
  ~ heal(15)
  "收" (shōu) — to harvest, to collect
* [Study the character patterns in the soil]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "种" (zhǒng) — to plant, seed, kind
* [Rest in the garden atmosphere]
  ~ heal(10)
  "园" (yuán) — garden, park
